# 1) Exclude hidden anywhere (first match wins)
- sh:**/.*
# 2) Explicit excludes
- sh:nas
- sh:nas/**
- sh:Downloads/**
- sh:.cache/**
- sh:.local/share/Trash/**
- sh:.thumbnails/**
- sh:.var/**
- sh:.npm/**
- sh:.cargo/**
- sh:.mozilla/**
- sh:go/**
# 3) Include everything else under ~
+ sh:**
# 4) Catch-all (anything not matched above is out)
- sh:**
